snippet.title: GensokyoDefenders(Switch,PS4) Trailer
snippet.description:
We released Gensokyo Defenders!! 

Use Traps and Spell Cards to fight back the magical masses in this Touhou Project fan game, now on the PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch!! 

Cirno, the ambitious icy fairy, has drawn attention from Aya, the Tengu reporter, who's been looking for the best scoop among the hoopla.
From Aya's camera, you will witness the journey of a weak, tiny icy fairy becoming the greatest of all!

PS4 - https://t.co/tTpmzTg4PZ
Switch - https://t.co/GzeMGRFVuS
